  "description": "A wide-angle, high-angle view showcases a sprawling urban landscape nestled alongside a vast body of water. The city is densely packed with buildings, appearing as a gray and beige patchwork from this distance. A long bridge or causeway extends into the water, connecting to a distant landmass. Above the city and water, dramatic, dark clouds dominate the sky, partially obscuring the sun which casts beams of light down onto the water's surface.  A forested hill with lush green vegetation occupies the foreground, framing the lower portion of the view. The lighting is dynamic, with areas of bright sunlight contrasting with the deep shadows cast by the clouds. The overall impression is one of scale and dramatic weather.",
